                            </p>
                            <div class="space-y-3 mb-8">
                                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                                    <span class="text-white/90 font-medium text-sm md:text-base">Franquicia tributaria SENCE</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                                    <span class="text-white/90 font-medium text-sm md:text-base">Programas adaptados a turnos operativos</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                                    <span class="text-white/90 font-medium text-sm md:text-base">Instructores acreditados</span>
